value.0: There are some people born into the world as a bitter root, and cause distress to many.  There are those who are born with a portion of love, and for a time, lighten the lives of those around them.  Vyper was born with so much love that her heart could not contain it all, and she lightened our lives here on Arelith for far too short a time before she left us.  Our sympathies to her family and friends, RIP Vyper, you will not be forgotten, but always missed.
